text: Annovka () is a rural locality (a village) in Zilairsky Selsoviet, Zilairsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 132 as of 2010. There are 4 streets. == Geography == It is located 12 km from Zilair. == References == Category:Rural localities in Zilairsky District
title: Annovka, Zilairsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
